🇵🇸🇵🇸🇵🇸 it’s wild bc I dropped this song on March 5th, 2023 (this video posted shortly after) yet I wrote it 2 years before. I get so consumed in my own life that I forget to zoom out. I forget that I have a platform however small or big , that I promised myself from day one I’d always use to speak out with. I’m sorry I haven’t posted anything yet , the cancel culture mindset in me was afraid that people would think i’d use atrocities like what’s happening across the sea for “content”. But, not showing my stance is just NOT an option. In my bio is a relief fund you can donate to, pls follow accounts like @eye.on.palestine @letstalkpalestine for more information. Stay informed!
